cz.cesnet.cloud.occi

Class Collection

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.cesnet.cloud.occi.Collection

  • public class Collection
extends Object
    Class representing a collection of OCCI instances. It can contain instances of classes Resource, Link and ActionInstance. Collection can be assigned a Model instance which will represent a OCCI model structure for all the instances in the collection.
    Author:
    Michal Kimle
